context.EnrolledIns.Join(context.Students, T1 => T1.StuId, T2 => T2.StuId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).Where(row => row.T2.CityCode == "NYC").Select(row => new { row.T1.Grade, row.T2.Age }).GroupBy(row => new { row.Age }).Select(group => new { group.Key.Age, MaxGrade = group.Select(row => row.Grade).Max(), MinGrade = group.Select(row => row.Grade).Min() }).OrderBy(group => group.Age).ToList();
context.Courses.Where(row => row.Credits == 3 || (row.Credits == 1 && row.Hours == "4")).Select(row => new { row.Cname }).ToList();
context.Departments.Where(row => row.Division == "AS" || row.Division == "EN" && row.Building == "NEB").Select(row => new { row.Dname }).ToList();
context.Students.Where(row =>!context.EnrolledIns.Select(row => row.StuId).Contains(row.StuId)).Select(row => new { row.Fname }).ToList();

context.GasStations.Join(context.StationCompanies, t2 => t2.StationId, t1 => t1.StationId, (t2, t1) => new { t2, t1 }).Join(context.Companies, joined => joined.t1.CompanyId, t3 => t3.CompanyId, (joined, t3) => new { joined.t2, joined.t1, t3 }).Where(row => row.t3.MarketValue > 100).Select(row => new { row.t2.Location }).ToList();

context.GasStations.Where(row => row.OpenYear > 2000).GroupBy(row => new { row.ManagerName }).OrderByDescending(group => group.Count()).Select(group => new { group.Key.ManagerName }).Take(1).ToList();
context.GasStations.OrderBy(row => row.OpenYear).Select(row => new { row.Location }).ToList();

context.Companies.Where(row => row.MainIndustry == "Banking").OrderBy(row => row.SalesBillion).OrderBy(row => row.ProfitsBillion).Select(row => new { row.Rank, row.Company1, row.MarketValue }).ToList();

context.Companies.OrderByDescending(row => row.AssetsBillion).Select(row => new { row.Company1, row.AssetsBillion }).Take(3).ToList().Select(row => context.StationCompanies.Where(row1 => row1.CompanyId == row.CompanyId).Select(row2 => new { row2.StationId, row2.RankOfTheYear }).Select(row3 => context.GasStations.Where(row4 => row3.StationId == row4.StationId).Select(row5 => new { row5.Location, row5.RepresentativeName })).ToList()[0]).Select(row => new { row.Location, row.RepresentativeName }).ToList();

context.Singers.Join(context.Songs, T1 => T1.SingerId, T2 => T2.SingerId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).GroupBy(row => new { row.T1.SingerId }).Where(group => group.Count() > 1).Select(group => new { group.Key.T1.Name }).ToList();

context.Singers.Join(context.Songs, T1 => T1.SingerId, T2 => T2.SingerId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).GroupBy(row => new { row.T1.SingerId }).Select(group => new { SingerName = group.Select(row => row.T1.Name).Distinct().First(), TotalSales = group.Sum(row => row.T2.Sales) }).ToList();
context.Singers.Where(row =>!context.Songs.Select(row => row.SingerId).Contains(row.SingerId)).Select(row => new { row.Name }).ToList();
context.Singers.Where(row => row.BirthYear < 1945 && row.BirthYear > 1955).Select(row => new { row.Citizenship }).Distinct().ToList();
context.HasPets.GroupBy(row => new { row.StuId }).Select(group => new { group.Key.StuId, Count = group.Count() }).ToList();

context.Students.Join(context.HasPets, T1 => T1.StuId, T2 => T2.StuId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).GroupBy(row => new { row.T1.StuId }).Select(group => new { group.Key.StuId, Count = group.Count() }).ToList();

context.Students.Join(context.HasPets, T1 => T1.StuId, T2 => T2.StuId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).GroupBy(row => new { row.T1.StuId }).Where(group => group.Count() > 1).Select(group => new { group.First().T1.Fname, group.First().T1.Sex }).ToList();

context.Students.Join(context.HasPets, T1 => T1.StuId, T2 => T2.StuId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).Join(context.Pets, joined => joined.T2.PetId, T3 => T3.PetId, (joined, T3) => new { joined.T1, joined.T2, T3 }).Where(row => row.T3.PetType == "Cat" && row.T3.PetAge == 3).Select(row => new { row.T1.Lname }).Take(1).ToList();
context.Students.Where(row =>!context.HasPets.Select(row => row.StuId).Contains(row.StuId)).Select(row => row.Age).Average();
context.Albums.OrderBy(row => row.Title).Select(row => new { row.Title }).ToList();

context.Artists.Join(context.Albums, T1 => T1.ArtistId, T2 => T2.ArtistId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).GroupBy(row => new { row.T1.ArtistId }).Where(group => group.Count() >= 3).OrderBy(group => group.Key.ArtistId).Select(group => new { group.Key.ArtistId, group.First().T1.Name }).ToList();
context.Artists.Where(row =>!context.Albums.Select(row => row.ArtistId).Contains(row.ArtistId)).Select(row => new { row.Name }).ToList();
context.Tracks.Join(context.Genres, T1 => T1.GenreId, T2 => T2.GenreId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).Where(row => row.T2.Name == "Rock").Select(row => row.T1.UnitPrice).Average();

context.Tracks.Join(context.Genres, T1 => T1.GenreId, T2 => T2.GenreId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).Where(row => row.T2.Name == "Pop").OrderBy(row => row.T1.Milliseconds).Select(row => new { row.T1.Milliseconds }).Distinct().Take(2).ToList();
context.Employees.Where(row => row.City == "Edmonton").Select(row => new { row.BirthDate }).ToList();
context.Tracks.Select(row => row.UnitPrice).Distinct().ToList();
context.Artists.Where(row =>!context.Albums.Select(row => row.ArtistId).Contains(row.ArtistId)).Count();

context.Albums.Join(context.Tracks, T1 => T1.AlbumId, T2 => T2.AlbumId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).Join(context.Genres, joined => joined.T2.GenreId, T3 => T3.GenreId, (joined, T3) => new { joined.T1, joined.T2, T3 }).Where(row => row.T3.Name == "Reggae" && row.T3.Name == "Rock").Select(row => row.T1.Title).ToList();

context.Authors.Join(context.Authorships, t1 => t1.AuthId, t2 => t2.AuthId, (t1, t2) => new { t1, t2 }).Join(context.Papers, joined => joined.t2.PaperId, t3 => t3.PaperId, (joined, t3) => new { joined.t1, joined.t2, t3 }).Where(row => row.t3.Title.Contains("Monadic")).Select(row => new { row.t1.Lname }).ToList();

context.Papers.Join(context.Authorships, T1 => T1.PaperId, T2 => T2.PaperId, (T1, T2) => new { T1, T2 }).GroupBy(row => new { row.T1.PaperId }).OrderByDescending(group => group.Count()).Select(group => new { group.First().T1.Title }).Take(1).ToList();
context.Authors.Where(row => row.Lname == "Ueno").Select(row => new { row.Fname }).ToList();
context.Authors.OrderByDescending(row => row.AuthOrder).Select(row => new { row.Lname }).Take(1).ToList();
context.Authors.OrderBy(row => row.Fname).Select(row => new { row.Fname }).ToList();
context.Authors.OrderBy(row => row.Lname).Select(row => new { row.Lname }).ToList();
context.Authors.OrderBy(row => row.Lname).Select(row => new { row.Lname, row.Fname }).ToList();
